  speakerName: "K\xF6yl\xFC"
  dialogueText: "H-Hakl\u0131s\u0131n rahip... Ama umut yok. Burada kapana k\u0131s\u0131ld\u0131k!
    Soka\u011F\u0131n ilerisini yarat\u0131klar ele ge\xE7irdi. Oraya giden hi\xE7
    kimse geri d\xF6nmedi.."
  choice1Text: "Korkmay\u0131n! Tanr\u0131'n\u0131n izniyle sizleri buradan \xE7\u0131karaca\u011F\u0131m."
  choice1NextNode: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3bfa76952d4347242b028d80bb1a2930, type: 2}
  choice2Text: "*\u0130\xE7inden* Tanr\u0131m bana g\xFC\xE7 ver."
